  '00000000-0000-0000-0001-000000000001',
  '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003',
  (SELECT id FROM subjects WHERE code = 'ENG_READING'),
  '수능 영어 독해 - 빈칸 추론 29·30번 완전 정복',
  '수능 영어 최고 난이도 빈칸 추론(29·30번) 전략을 실전 지문으로 훈련합니다.',
  'Today we are going to master blank inference questions, which are the most difficult in the English section. The key strategy is to identify the main argument of the passage first, then find the blank that serves as the core idea. For example, in a passage about delayed gratification: "The ability to delay gratification is one of the most powerful predictors of success in life." The blank typically completes the central claim. Common distractors include options that are partially related but contradict the logical flow. Always use the surrounding context-especially topic sentences and concluding sentences-to confirm your answer. Remember: the correct answer must be logically consistent with the entire passage, not just the surrounding sentence.',
  ARRAY['ENG_READ_INFER_BLANK', 'ENG_READ_MAIN'],
  'done',
