  1,
  E'[지문] Exercise has long been known to benefit physical health, but recent research suggests its impact extends far beyond the body. Regular physical activity has been shown to improve mood, reduce anxiety, and enhance cognitive function.\n\n[문제] 윗글의 주제로 가장 적절한 것은?',
